{"version":"2026-05-16T12.15.26","description":"APKDeepLens 是一种基于 Python 的工具，旨在扫描 Android 应用程序（APK 文件）以查找安全漏洞。它专门针对 OWASP 十大移动漏洞，为开发人员、渗透测试人员和安全研究人员提供了一种简单有效的方法来评估 Android 应用程序的安全状况。","notes":["【工具类型】: Android工具","【主要功能】: APKDeepLens 是一种基于 Python 的工具，旨在扫描 Android 应用程序（APK 文件）以查找安全漏洞。它专门针对 OWASP 十大移动漏洞，为开发人员、渗透测试人员和安全研究人员提供了一种简单有效的方法来评估 Android 应用程序的安全状况。","【适用场景】: 根据描述推断的适用场景","【技术特点】: Android平台相关工具"],"homepage":"https://github.com/d78ui98/APKDeepLens","license":"UNKNOWN","suggest":{"python":"miniconda3"},"url":"https://github.com/d78ui98/APKDeepLens/archive/refs/heads/master.zip","hash":"","pre_install":["Set-Content \"$dir\\APKDeepLens.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0","@call activate python3env","@python \"APKDeepLens.py\" %*","@popd' -Encoding Ascii"],"post_install":"& cmd /c \"call activate python3env && pip install -r $dir\\requirements.txt\"","extract_dir":"APKDeepLens-main","bin":"APKDeepLens.bat","checkver":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/d78ui98/APKDeepLens/commits","regex":"([\\d-]+T)(\\d+):(\\d+):(\\d+)","replace":"$1$2.$3.$4"},"autoupdate":{"url":"https://github.com/d78ui98/APKDeepLens/archive/refs/heads/master.zip"},"from":"https://github.com/bright-angel/scoop-bucket"}
